      • getBestEffortIsolatedKey

        public static String getBestEffortIsolatedKey(Class<?> commandClass)
        Returns a command key with the higehst possible (best effort) level of user and tenant isolation. If the user is not authenticated, a tenant-isolated command key is returned. If the tenant is not available, a global command key is returned.
